                    <note xml:lang="en" type="abstract" xml:id="abstract-en-1117">Aday was commemorated by <persName ref="http://syriaca.org/person/74">John of Ephesus</persName> in his Lives of the Eastern
          Saints. He built twelve monasteries with his brother <persName ref="http://syriaca.org/person/1548">Abraham</persName>.</note>
                    <note xml:lang="en" type="disambiguation" source="#bib1117-1">According to Fiey this is not the same as the <persName ref="http://syriaca.org/person/1116">Addai the Chorepiscopus</persName> mentioned in <title ref="http://syriaca.org/work/800">Addai the Chorepiscopus (text)</title>.</note>
